  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't Sleep plunges players into a heart-pounding horror experience set in a dark and foreboding bedroom infested with malevolent monsters. As night falls, players must navigate the eerie environment, using cunning and strategy to outwit the lurking creatures and survive until dawn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suspenseful Atmosphere</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an atmospheric and suspenseful gameplay experience that will test your nerves and keep you guessing as you navigate the nightmarish bedroom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/631948388c3e8cddd3e0cb066190b9d9.poster.avif?t=1750062993\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/631948388c3e8cddd3e0cb066190b9d9.webm?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/631948388c3e8cddd3e0cb066190b9d9.mp4?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize cunning and decision-making skills to outsmart the creatures that lurk in the shadows, ensuring your survival through the long night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/f26e8be5e2d28151e37f9386ef65e917.poster.avif?t=1750062993\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/f26e8be5e2d28151e37f9386ef65e917.webm?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/f26e8be5e2d28151e37f9386ef65e917.mp4?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Terrifying Monster Encounters</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face off against a variety of bone-chilling monsters that lurk in the shadows, each with its own unique abilities and behaviors that will keep you on your toes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/e989199b532c743506052751015e0efc.poster.avif?t=1750062993\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/e989199b532c743506052751015e0efc.webm?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/e989199b532c743506052751015e0efc.mp4?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't Sleep plunges players into a heart-pounding horror experience set in a dark and foreboding bedroom infested with malevolent monsters. As night falls, players must navigate the eerie environment, using cunning and strategy to outwit the lurking creatures and survive until dawn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Suspenseful Atmosphere</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in an atmospheric and suspenseful gameplay experience that will test your nerves and keep you guessing as you navigate the nightmarish bedroom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/631948388c3e8cddd3e0cb066190b9d9.poster.avif?t=1750062993\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/631948388c3e8cddd3e0cb066190b9d9.webm?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/631948388c3e8cddd3e0cb066190b9d9.mp4?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Gameplay</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize cunning and decision-making skills to outsmart the creatures that lurk in the shadows, ensuring your survival through the long night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/f26e8be5e2d28151e37f9386ef65e917.poster.avif?t=1750062993\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3491070/extras/f26e8be5e2d28151e37f9386ef65e917.webm?t=1750062993\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https:/